snippet.title: Blue Fire Void of Sorrows DLC Trailer
snippet.description:
FREE Blue Fire DLC is now available on Nintendo Switch, Xbox and PC! The Void of Sorrows expansion features two new areas with a new boss, 16 Voids, ducks and more. 



Void of Sorrows will soon be available in the PlayStation and Stadia versions. 


#BlueFire #NintendoSwitch #Steam #Xbox
